  {
    "id": "amnesia",
    "name": "Amnesia",
    "category": "Head & Neck",
    "emotionalRoot": "Extreme trauma survival, severe emotional overload, and a self-preservational mental block designed to hide memories or information that would otherwise shatter your emotional stability.",
    "metaphor": "Your mind's protective mechanism temporarily withdrawing access to the memory mainframe, which may reflect a symbolic pattern of protection when looking at painful truths.",
